name: Ley, Sussan Penelope MP
content: Ms LEY (Farrerâ€”Deputy Leader of the Opposition) (15:28): In accordance with standing order 105(b), I wish to draw your attention to the 10 questions in writing asked of the Minister for Small Business which remain unanswered. I ask you, Mr Speaker, to write to the Minister for Small Business, seeking reasons for the delay in answering, especially given her absolute incompetence last year.
